a slightly stronger result: this result holds as long as $|E|\\geq\nCq^{7/3}$. Furthermore, when $d=2$ the result holds when $|E|\\geq Cq^{7/4}$.\nHere, $C$ is a function of $d$ and thus constant with respect to $q$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 17:03:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-07"}
