anetary interiors could lose a substantial portion of their N and C\ninventories with increasing degrees of thermal metamorphism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 22:14:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-10"}
