uces from near coronal to near\nphotospheric values during the rising phase of the flare and recovers back to\ncoronal values during decay phase, which is also consistent with the\nchromospheric evaporation scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 07:14:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
