modes. These findings pave the way for halide perovskites as a\nnext-generation platform for tunable anisotropic photonics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 13:26:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
