 information about the location of the\nRISs. Finally, through numerical analysis of the EFIM and its smallest\neigenvalue, we demonstrate the loss in information when the far-field model is\n{\\em incorrectly} applied to the signals received at a UE experiencing\nnear-field propagation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 14:57:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-10"}
